name: Arco Design Mobile Components
description:
📮 Arco 移动端组件资源发布！

Arco Design Mobile 提供了 50+ 基础组件

随着 Arco Design Mobile 的开源，我们希望在持续获取意见和建议并进行迭代的同时鼓励社区共建，使组件更易用、功能更强大、使用者更广泛。


Arco Mobile Component resource is officially released!

Arco Design Mobile provides 50+ components， we want to encourage community building as we continue to iterate on ideas and suggestions to make components easier to use, more powerful, and more widely available.


📅 Github：https://github.com/arco-design/arco-design-mobile


📪 官网：https://arco.design/mobile/react
